                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[07.10.2009]</p>
                <p>Continued focus on solidarity, value creation and social justice. This was how Prime Minister Jens Stoltenberg, Finance Minister Kristin Halvorsen and Minister of Transport and Communications Liv Signe Navarsete summed up the majority Government’s new policy platform at Soria Moria today. Employment, education, welfare and climate change were singled out as priority areas for the next four years. </p>
                
                
